OL,5, US real estate heir Robert Durst,      
OL,6, subject of HBO crime documentary series
OL,7, The Jinx, has been sentenced to life in
OL,8, prison for killing his best friend.    
OL,10,FDurst was found guilty of killing Susan
OL,11,FBerman in 2000 to stop her talking to  
OL,12,Fpolice about his wife's disappearance. 
OL,14,FThen aged 55, she was found shot in the
OL,15,Fhead in her Beverly Hills home. Police 
OL,16,Fbelieve he killed two others as well.  
OL,18,FIn a victim impact statement in court, 
OL,19,FBerman's son told Durst "you murdered  
OL,20,Fthe person I was" when he killed her.  
